column5: Expierenced some very good fishing last fall (Oct) in the bay, was the first time. What's the fishing like in the spring? Thanks in advance! Steve
some years it is ok, for numbers, others poor not a spring destination for me big fish are usually gone
Hey Steve, what I have heard is they are still there now, and will be gone before the ice leaves. Springtime we need to look at the St Louis River - Duluth.
